SUMMARY:Dillsburg Game Night March Long Game Day
DESCRIPTION:Central PA Game Club\nLong Game Day in Dillsburg\, we usually 
 have about 50 people. Show up anytime. Starts at 2pm. Bring a few dollars 
 for pizza and we will order it for dinner around 6pm. Games until whenever
 ! We usually do Blood on the Clock Tower at the end of the night. Friendly
  group\, come alone or bring a group.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/centralpagameclub/events/313290371/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
